The paper deals with the problem of multi-label classification, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper proposes a new approach to multi-label classification that allows for partial abstention, which is a novel contribution to the field. The paper also discusses the theoretical and experimental results of this approach. Given these factors, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
